{"tid":2217630,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警員拍片屈民主黨派錢示威 投訴警察課立案循行為失當調查","createTime":"2020-09-25T14:41:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T14:41:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"03e4c60ecb42d583d79aa633f95c25c101c748a2","tid":2217630,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:41:38.000Z","msg":"今年３月中西區區議會主席鄭麗琼，被警方以涉煽動意圖拘捕，鄭的民主黨黨友在警署外就鄭的保釋金「夾錢」時疑被警員拍攝，其後建制陣營流傳短片指民主黨向聲援鄭的人士派錢。民主黨中西區區議員甘乃威表示，投訴警察課通知會立案調查事件，並循涉嫌有警員行為失當的方向調查，不過甘坦言對調查「沒有期望也不會失望」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/LGNPZF4M3BCTPGNOVJ7U7BP6CU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2FLGNPZF4M3BCTPGNOVJ7U7BP6CU%2F&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzlT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=00eaa8ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2FLGNPZF4M3BCTPGNOVJ7U7BP6CU%2F&h=79515605\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/LGNPZF4M3BCTPGNOVJ7U7BP6CU/</a>"}]}